<li class='playlist-talks__talk' data-talk-id='2219' id='talk-2219'>
<div class='playlist-talks__talk__wrapper'>
<div class='playlist-talks__talk__content'>
<a class='playlist-talks__thumb playlist-talks__play' href='/talks/anand_giridharadas_a_tale_of_two_americas_and_the_mini_mart_where_they_collided' target='_blank'>
<span class="thumb thumb--video thumb--crop-top thumb--autoplay"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" autoplay="autoplay" class=" thumb__image" crop="top" play="1163" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpe-a.akamaihd.net/images/ted/a2b28c69eac9216fa175749c32ced0c39d6c93ff_2880x1620.jpg?quality=70&amp;w=300" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span><span class="thumb__duration">19:23</span></span>
<div class='playlist-talks__thumb__indicator'>Now playing</div>
</a>
<div class='playlist-talks__meta'>
<span class='playlist-talks__speaker'>
<a class="playlist-talks__speaker__link" href="/speakers/anand_giridharadas" target="_blank">Anand Giridharadas</a></span>
<h9 class='playlist-talks__title'>
<a class='playlist-talks__play' href='/talks/anand_giridharadas_a_tale_of_two_americas_and_the_mini_mart_where_they_collided' target='_blank'>
A tale of two Americas. And the mini-mart where they collided
</a>
</h9>
</div>
<div class='playlist-talks__info'>
<div class='playlist-talks__description m5'>
Ten days after 9/11, a shocking attack at a Texas mini-mart shattered the lives of two men: the victim and the attacker. In this stunning talk, Anand Giridharadas, author of "The True American," tells the story of what happened next. It's a parable about the two paths an American life can take, and a powerful call for reconciliation.
</div>
