<div class='playlist-talks__thumb__indicator'>Now playing</div>
</a>
<div class='playlist-talks__meta'>
<span class='playlist-talks__speaker'>
<a class="playlist-talks__speaker__link" href="/speakers/colin_grant" target="_blank">Colin Grant</a></span>
<h9 class='playlist-talks__title'>
<a class='playlist-talks__play' href='/talks/colin_grant_the_son_of_a_difficult_father' target='_blank'>
How our stories cross over
</a>
</h9>
</div>
<div class='playlist-talks__info'>
<div class='playlist-talks__description m5'>
Colin Grant has spent a lifetime navigating the emotional landscape between his father’s world and his own. Born in England to Jamaican parents, Grant draws on stories of shared experience within his immigrant community — and reflects on how he found forgiveness for a father who rejected him.
</div>
